{"tid":2153972,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"耗時七年自費全手繪動畫電影「音樂」 BD/DVD 12月發售","createTime":"2020-08-13T01:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T01:09:13.000Z","uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02d6c760f6b2f104937ced89bfda4e9df5328078","tid":2153972,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T01:01:56.000Z","msg":"アニメ映画「音楽」BD / DVDが12月発売、同日に古美術のアルバムもリリース<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/6758f1218ab6392213784fb40578e1ca76bf04bd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.yahoo.co.jp%2Farticles%2F6758f1218ab6392213784fb40578e1ca76bf04bd&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7ctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=6949d7cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/6758f1218ab6392213784fb40578e1ca76bf04bd</a><br />\n<br />\n 劇情大綱<br />\n<br />\n成天遊手好閒的高中生三人組研二、太田與朝倉，在學校不是打電動，就是與隔壁學校幫派釘孤枝。一天晚上，研二意外受一位搖滾樂手的義行感召，下定決心獻身音樂界，於是召集太田和朝倉組了搖滾樂團。三人對音樂一竅不通，也沒有玩過樂器，卻搖滾魂上身，找來貝斯與大鼓，開始熱血樂團人生，更想不到他們竟還受邀前進音樂祭！三個中二的搖滾處男能不能迎接這個大挑戰？改編自大橋裕之漫畫《音樂和漫畫》，歷時七年製作，甚至實地前往音樂祭現場拍攝取材，以獨特的幽默感呈現身懷熱血的搖滾魂！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7Fh6prMlXFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7Fh6prMlXFg&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7ctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=3f1a4ba8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7Fh6prMlXFg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eRzbslTm-Yc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeRzbslTm-Yc&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7ctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=ed594b23\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eRzbslTm-Yc</a>"},{"pid":"8b58bb204eed58ec5e40bdee4e9024cf9b7ca105","tid":2153972,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T01:03:15.000Z","msg":"《搖滾吧！中二樂團》動畫監製松江哲明專訪 分享耗時七年的製作幕後花絮<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=187571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fgnn%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D187571&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7ctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=c7a019e4\" t